Do,arena estas main module for test battle structure of our excellent game, and this so-called arena is necessary to do this(test) good.

PLayer can manipulate arena per consol input.

#################
#       |       #
# G H I | G H I #
#       |       #
# D E F | D E F #
#       |       #
# A B C | A B C #
#       |       #
#################

user can use manage comands, and act comands: manage to change battlefield, str enemies, spawn enemies, e.t.c.
act comands - simulates round.
